title: BruteForce
description:
BruteForce is a powerful SaaS starter kit designed to help developers launch faster by providing a complete, ready-to-use foundation. With cutting-edge technologies like SvelteKit with Svelte5 (Runes), shadcn/ui, and PocketBase, Bruteforce covers everything from frontend to backend and beyond.

BruteForce gives you the tools to hit the ground running. Get instant access to the Git repository, future updates, and fast chat support to ensure a smooth development experience.
